  "": "The film takes place in an isolated mansion at the Scottish Highlands, where Jack, a young escort gets into a fight with one of his male clients and seemingly accidentally kills him. He runs off and hides in room 14, a secluded wing where the wealthy but mentally unstable man Malcolm lives. Malcolm offers him refuge from the police, liquor, pills and as many male prostitutes as he wishes. 
Jack then discovers that Malcolm records everything on video. He explains that he is so lonely and unstable that he can no longer have sex with anyone else, but still likes to watch others do it. He offers Jack much money to fulfil his sexual fantasies for him, so he can watch. Slowly but surely the fantasies get more perverted and masochistic, until Malcolm offers Jack to participate in a live-action role-play where they both pretend to be serial killers. In exchange for much money they search for the best potential male actor.
